WEBVTT

01:38.400 --> 01:40.520
EPISODE 15

01:41.240 --> 01:42.520
Recently, we have reviewed

01:42.600 --> 01:44.680
classic documentaries
from around the world.

01:44.760 --> 01:47.760
Now, we'll put the knowledge to work,

01:47.840 --> 01:49.880
by making a short documentary.

01:50.240 --> 01:52.960
The theme is the graduation season.

01:53.320 --> 01:55.400
I'm looking for a student

01:55.640 --> 01:58.480
to volunteer and make this documentary.

02:06.760 --> 02:07.880
How come as soon as I said, "volunteer,"

02:07.960 --> 02:09.919
- you all lower your heads?
- Cao Guang!

02:10.000 --> 02:11.680
Scoot over!

02:14.600 --> 02:16.200
Then move and let me get in.

02:19.440 --> 02:23.120
Why do I find this scene familiar?

02:23.880 --> 02:25.640
- We're making a documentary...
- Hey!

02:25.720 --> 02:27.400
Don't pretend you can't hear me!

02:27.480 --> 02:28.680
Do you still want my help with Weiwei?

02:29.960 --> 02:30.800
Shut up!

02:31.440 --> 02:34.080
Shut up? Why are you so mean?

02:34.240 --> 02:35.680
You asked for my help,

02:35.760 --> 02:37.320
now you want me to shut up.

02:37.800 --> 02:40.160
You know you have no chance,
so embarrassment turned to anger.

02:40.240 --> 02:41.360
Why are you so petty?

02:41.440 --> 02:43.440
- Why are you so...
- What?

02:45.280 --> 02:47.440
You, over there, stand up.

02:50.160 --> 02:53.200
- He asked you to get up.
- It's you!

02:55.200 --> 02:56.440
Both of you, stand up.

03:07.480 --> 03:12.560
Despite being an elective class,
as long as it's a classroom,

03:12.640 --> 03:15.520
the lead actor is the professor,
passing down knowledge.

03:16.240 --> 03:18.000
You have to work with the lead actor,

03:18.480 --> 03:21.520
while playing your own parts, right?

03:24.400 --> 03:26.920
You two seem to be fighting the lead actor
for the spotlight in every class.

03:27.280 --> 03:28.120
Fine.

03:28.200 --> 03:31.800
I'll let you two be the lead actors
in this class.

03:32.880 --> 03:34.280
Professor, it's a misunderstanding.

03:34.600 --> 03:38.280
I only want to find a seat
and listen to the lecture quietly.

03:38.360 --> 03:42.440
You're 20 minutes late to the film.
Don't you think it's a shame?

03:42.920 --> 03:44.960
Aside from missing the beginning,

03:45.040 --> 03:47.200
you distract those
who are already watching.

03:47.840 --> 03:49.800
Attending a class is the same
as watching a film.

03:50.000 --> 03:52.600
Miss the beginning, and you lose the plot.

03:53.560 --> 03:54.640
Don't be late again.

03:55.800 --> 03:57.960
- I won't, Professor.
- Good.

03:58.840 --> 04:02.200
You two are now in charge of
filming the documentary

04:02.280 --> 04:03.360
for the graduation gala.

04:13.400 --> 04:16.360
CAMPUS RECRUITMENT

04:19.279 --> 04:20.880
RECRUITMENT

04:27.640 --> 04:30.640
RECRUITING TALENTS,
GREAT BENEFITS OFFERED

04:40.360 --> 04:42.920
We've shot a lot of footage.
Can we wrap it up?

04:43.240 --> 04:45.360
No, we haven't done the interviews.

04:46.320 --> 04:48.640
If we don't go now,
the cafeteria will run out of food.

04:49.960 --> 04:51.480
All you do is eat.

05:08.640 --> 05:10.600
That's not fair! There's no justice!

05:11.840 --> 05:13.200
You said, you're afraid of messing up,

05:13.280 --> 05:15.280
so you only want brainless chores.

05:15.400 --> 05:18.120
There were many small tripods
in the equipment room.

05:18.200 --> 05:20.920
Why must you borrow
this big old heavy one?

05:21.000 --> 05:24.720
Plus, is your dingy camera
good enough for this big guy?

05:25.280 --> 05:27.320
Professionally speaking,
that's the most stable one.

05:27.400 --> 05:28.240
Don't you know anything?

05:30.080 --> 05:31.080
I won't do it!

05:32.240 --> 05:36.120
You're rebelling, tough.
Then you do the shooting.

05:40.880 --> 05:43.520
I'm hungry. I can't carry it.

05:44.160 --> 05:46.480
Lady, it's all your fault

05:46.560 --> 05:48.720
I have to make
this graduation documentary.

05:48.920 --> 05:51.240
Now I have a lousy teammate.
Enough's enough!

05:51.600 --> 05:52.600
What did you say?

05:52.800 --> 05:55.600
Nothing. It's crowded there.
Let's go do interviews.

05:57.240 --> 05:59.000
Production assistant, please hurry.

05:59.080 --> 06:00.920
Go set up the tripod.

06:16.120 --> 06:18.720
Okay, go stand there.
I'll adjust the focus.

06:21.240 --> 06:25.080
I'm the production assistant,
not the model. I'm not going.

06:26.000 --> 06:28.440
Will you hurry? The sun will set soon.

06:28.520 --> 06:29.720
We're not eating until we're done.

06:32.200 --> 06:34.520
No, I'm camera shy.

06:35.360 --> 06:37.600
I see. That makes sense.

06:37.680 --> 06:40.160
If I looked like you,
I'd be camera shy, too.

06:41.440 --> 06:44.560
Fine, if you're camera shy,

06:44.640 --> 06:48.160
turn your back to the camera.
Focus on the bigger picture.

07:07.360 --> 07:10.360
Are you done? You're taking forever.

07:10.880 --> 07:11.920
Done.

07:17.960 --> 07:19.000
What do you want to borrow?

07:19.520 --> 07:22.440
A few programming books
to study over the summer break.

07:30.760 --> 07:34.680
The two-month summer vacation
is coming up.

07:38.400 --> 07:39.440
I picked these for you.

07:41.320 --> 07:44.280
Will they be too difficult?
Don't pick them based on your level.

07:44.360 --> 07:46.960
Don't worry.
I can tutor you via the internet.

07:51.800 --> 07:54.240
My only regret
in the past four years of college

07:54.320 --> 07:56.360
is that I never fell in love.

07:56.640 --> 07:58.720
If I could do it over,

07:59.600 --> 08:02.560
I'd go to a teaching college,
where there are more girls.

08:10.600 --> 08:12.920
- Thanks for doing the interview.
- Sure.

08:14.840 --> 08:18.520
- Zhao Erxi, get the tripod. Let's go!
- Come here, Weiwei!

08:18.840 --> 08:21.000
Let's go, Zhao Erxi.

08:21.280 --> 08:23.840
Hold on, let's interview them.

08:24.240 --> 08:27.680
Department belle and school heartthrob,
a couple made in heaven.

08:27.920 --> 08:29.920
If they appear in the video,

08:30.000 --> 08:33.200
it'll be a huge hit
at the graduation gala.

08:34.520 --> 08:38.200
- Fortune favors me!
- I don't want to film the likes of them.

08:39.400 --> 08:42.120
Don't let your personal feelings
affect the work.

08:43.320 --> 08:46.000
Who told me
to focus on the bigger picture?

08:53.040 --> 08:56.880
Weiwei, can I interview you and Lord?

08:57.120 --> 08:58.440
You can talk about anything,

08:58.520 --> 09:02.360
like graduation, work, ideals,
anything you want.

09:04.120 --> 09:07.440
Of course, it's even better,
if you talk about your relationship.

09:08.320 --> 09:11.680
Erxi, you know
I'm not good at these things.

09:12.560 --> 09:16.520
Weiwei, I depend on you
to pass my elective class.

09:21.560 --> 09:22.600
Sure.

09:25.400 --> 09:27.040
Production assistant! Set up the camera!

09:39.160 --> 09:42.880
- Where's the record button, Cao Guang?
- I don't know.

09:45.560 --> 09:48.280
Sorry, hold on a second.
Let me figure it out.

10:03.640 --> 10:05.040
Go ahead, Weiwei.

10:05.760 --> 10:08.760
Wait, you should let Lord speak.

10:09.800 --> 10:11.600
You're his girlfriend.

10:11.680 --> 10:13.920
Maybe you can share your feelings

10:14.000 --> 10:15.520
on your boyfriend leaving school?

10:17.040 --> 10:20.760
Erxi, he's still nearby,
even after graduation.

10:22.040 --> 10:26.080
That's good. Displaying your affection
is one way to commemorate graduation.

10:30.960 --> 10:32.360
I'm not done yet!

10:35.560 --> 10:37.680
Weiwei. Lord. See you.

10:40.640 --> 10:43.240
Wait up, Cao Guang!

10:47.600 --> 10:48.440
"All your life"?

10:52.800 --> 10:56.400
No, he only gave me a flier once.

11:05.440 --> 11:09.400
Server, I'll have
a Salt and Pepper Pork Strips,

11:09.480 --> 11:12.320
a Fish with Pickled Vegetables,
two bowls of rice,

11:13.080 --> 11:14.680
and a Kung Pao Chicken.

11:14.760 --> 11:16.120
Can't you order any vegetables?

11:17.320 --> 11:19.880
You made me carry heavy equipment all day,

11:19.960 --> 11:22.000
and you want me to eat less? No way!

11:22.440 --> 11:24.560
I'll have a West Lake Beef Soup.

11:24.640 --> 11:26.080
That'll be all. Thanks.

11:27.720 --> 11:28.680
How boring.

11:29.560 --> 11:33.080
That's for me. Also, we're going Dutch.

11:33.440 --> 11:35.840
Of course! You think I'd let you pay?

11:36.560 --> 11:38.440
Server! I'll have two bottles of booze.

11:54.600 --> 11:56.680
Here, it's my treat.

11:57.520 --> 11:58.640
That can wait.

11:58.720 --> 12:00.720
You should let Lord speak.

12:02.640 --> 12:03.960
Weiwei's footage? Let me see.

12:07.480 --> 12:08.320
What are you doing?

12:08.680 --> 12:10.840
I'm deleting it. It's poorly shot.

12:10.920 --> 12:12.440
It'll take up storage space,
and we won't use it.

12:12.920 --> 12:16.840
No, you can't delete it.
I want to keep it.

12:21.400 --> 12:22.440
You won't grab it now?

12:23.720 --> 12:26.520
Well... It's not my fault.

12:26.600 --> 12:28.720
Why did you delete Weiwei's footage?

12:29.480 --> 12:31.360
Oh, no! It's soaked through.

12:33.920 --> 12:36.560
No way! What if it's broken?

12:38.960 --> 12:41.680
This camera costs more than 10,000.
You'll have to pay.

12:43.640 --> 12:45.520
I don't have the money.
Why should I pay for it?

12:45.760 --> 12:46.760
You grabbed it.

12:46.960 --> 12:47.800
Well...

12:49.000 --> 12:50.400
You ordered the West Lake Beef Soup.

12:50.480 --> 12:51.800
You're responsible, too.

12:53.160 --> 12:54.680
We split the bill. Is that fair?

13:00.240 --> 13:03.120
- But I don't have the money.
- Wait, I said...

13:06.440 --> 13:09.960
It's just wet.
Let it dry on the porch tomorrow.

13:10.440 --> 13:12.520
- Maybe it'll be fine.
- Don't turn it on!

13:13.720 --> 13:15.640
I fixed the camera!

13:19.920 --> 13:21.080
What's wrong?

13:21.840 --> 13:25.360
What's wrong? Simply put, it's fried.

13:25.440 --> 13:27.520
You're doomed, Zhao Erxi!

14:06.080 --> 14:08.640
The exams are over, finally! We're free!

14:09.840 --> 14:10.680
In September,

14:10.760 --> 14:14.040
we'll get a new batch of young men
when school starts.

14:15.240 --> 14:17.480
Erxi, I used your line.

14:17.560 --> 14:19.360
Why don't you chime in?

14:19.680 --> 14:21.320
I don't want to talk.

14:21.600 --> 14:22.720
What's wrong?

14:23.560 --> 14:27.000
I'm wondering how I'm going to repay
the rest of my debt.

14:27.080 --> 14:29.600
Don't mind her. She's crazy.

14:31.040 --> 14:34.040
Everyone, let's have a quick meeting

14:34.120 --> 14:36.160
on your summer internship.

14:37.800 --> 14:41.000
That's right! I have my summer internship
at Zhenyi Tech!

14:41.200 --> 14:43.120
You got into Zhenyi, Erxi?

14:43.200 --> 14:44.160
You're good!

14:44.520 --> 14:47.120
I hear interns get paid 100 bucks a day.

14:48.480 --> 14:49.880
100 bucks a day?

14:50.560 --> 14:54.000
The notice I got said the internship
is for a month, starting August 1.

14:54.080 --> 14:57.720
30 days come to 3,000 bucks!

14:58.000 --> 15:02.080
Weiwei, I'm rich! I'm so rich!

15:02.160 --> 15:06.560
Enough. Be quiet. Will you listen to me?

15:08.800 --> 15:11.280
Let me borrow your phone. I'll text Lord.

15:13.440 --> 15:16.440
Why doesn't he buy you a cellphone?

15:17.440 --> 15:20.640
This boyfriend of yours is so...
insensitive.

15:20.720 --> 15:23.160
Doesn't he know that
once you have a phone,

15:23.480 --> 15:25.840
it'll help bring you two closer?

15:26.040 --> 15:29.200
We've only known each other for a while.
He's not the type to do that.

15:29.800 --> 15:31.240
That'd be awkward.

15:45.160 --> 15:46.440
When did you get here?

15:47.240 --> 15:48.080
Just now.

15:51.600 --> 15:55.840
We had a meeting after the exam,
about our summer internship.

15:56.080 --> 15:57.640
I texted you from Xiaoling's phone.

15:58.200 --> 16:00.000
Let's go. They should be waiting for us.

16:03.320 --> 16:05.120
It's our get-together. Did you forget?

16:08.320 --> 16:09.960
Is it your treat again?

16:11.840 --> 16:12.680
What else?

16:15.360 --> 16:16.840
Come take a look!

16:16.920 --> 16:18.960
Why do I say this blanket is good?

16:19.040 --> 16:22.160
Because ever since I started using it,
I haven't flunked a class.

16:22.360 --> 16:26.040
Why is that? This blanket is good luck.
Come check it out.

16:26.880 --> 16:29.400
Hey there, young lady.
Come check out my blanket.

16:29.480 --> 16:30.840
Why do I say this blanket is good?

16:31.200 --> 16:34.000
Because ever since I started using it,
I haven't flunked a class.

16:34.080 --> 16:35.600
It's a good luck blanket.

16:36.720 --> 16:38.600
It's fashionable
to use a graduating senior's blanket.

16:38.680 --> 16:40.120
Come check it out.

16:41.440 --> 16:45.040
Mr. Girly, don't pick up bad behavior
from others!

16:49.480 --> 16:52.760
My disguise is impeccable.
How did you recognize me?

16:53.960 --> 16:57.000
Your elegance is so remarkable.

16:57.080 --> 16:59.920
No sunglasses, hats, or masks
can conceal it.

17:01.840 --> 17:04.560
You do have a point there, young lady.

17:05.720 --> 17:08.760
You see, I'm simply too naive.

17:09.319 --> 17:12.000
It's rare to run into someone
who truly gets me.

17:12.160 --> 17:16.200
I'll give you this blanket for free.

17:21.200 --> 17:22.040
Are you jealous?

17:23.319 --> 17:24.160
Not at all.

17:25.240 --> 17:27.599
Drop the act. Why else would you stop me?

17:28.119 --> 17:29.400
You're engaging in false advertising.

17:32.240 --> 17:36.080
Freshman year, Marxist philosophy,
you flunked twice.

17:36.960 --> 17:40.000
Wait, why would you remember
embarrassing stuff like that?

17:40.560 --> 17:41.840
Don't listen to his nonsense.

17:47.160 --> 17:49.680
Got it. We'll be right there.

17:52.000 --> 17:54.200
Houzi is waiting for us
at House of Tianxiang.

17:54.960 --> 17:58.720
Wait. Why go to
House of Tianxiang all the time?

17:59.680 --> 18:02.160
Call Houzi and Yugong. Today,

18:02.240 --> 18:06.800
I'm taking you all to a fine-dining place.

18:10.240 --> 18:13.920
- Is this it?
- Yeah, what's this place?

18:14.960 --> 18:19.320
Immortals, not height, make a peak famous;
dragons, not depth, make a lake magical.

18:19.400 --> 18:20.920
This house may be humble...

18:21.920 --> 18:24.040
Forget it. You won't get it anyway.

18:24.120 --> 18:26.880
What I mean to say is,
this eatery is delicious.

18:28.360 --> 18:29.200
Here it is!

18:29.720 --> 18:32.600
My friend's Fish with Pickled Vegetables
is the best in the world.

18:32.680 --> 18:35.400
Try it. If you like it,
tell your friends to come.

18:37.240 --> 18:39.600
These are my roommates
and the girlfriend of one.

18:39.680 --> 18:42.160
You're working here all summer?

18:43.040 --> 18:43.880
Yes.

18:44.560 --> 18:48.640
Great! I'll ask them to come often
and bring you business.

18:49.120 --> 18:51.120
- You don't have to do that.
- What?

18:52.800 --> 18:55.240
I'm not the owner. I'm exhausted.

18:57.360 --> 18:58.440
That's true.

19:00.960 --> 19:02.440
You should come by yourself.

19:04.600 --> 19:07.600
Okay! I won't recommend it
to random people.

19:15.840 --> 19:18.600
It is good.
Mei's recommendation checks out.

19:18.920 --> 19:19.960
Pretty good...

19:21.320 --> 19:25.360
Are you pigs or what? Just this bit...

19:25.520 --> 19:26.600
I saved you some.

19:28.280 --> 19:30.520
See, Ms. Weiwei is the best.

19:31.560 --> 19:34.520
In this moment, I feel motherly love.

19:37.920 --> 19:39.520
Take your time. Don't choke.

19:41.360 --> 19:45.760
Having a girlfriend brings out
Nai's humanity. He cares about me now.

19:46.920 --> 19:47.880
It's fatherly love.

19:57.480 --> 20:00.480
This place is awesome.
It's delicious and inexpensive.

20:00.560 --> 20:02.040
We should come often.

20:02.120 --> 20:05.400
But there's one problem.
We're letting Nai off easy today.

20:05.640 --> 20:08.280
I was hoping to get
an expensive meal out of him, right?

20:08.720 --> 20:10.200
It's good, come often.

20:12.000 --> 20:14.200
You mean they should get
more free meals out of me?

20:16.640 --> 20:20.120
I said it too fast. I meant,
it's a good place, they should come often.

20:21.360 --> 20:23.040
Thanks, everyone.

20:23.120 --> 20:25.680
Don't come too often.
It tires out the cook.

20:25.760 --> 20:29.120
No way!
A promise made is a promise kept.

20:29.520 --> 20:31.440
Here, let's drink to this spirit.

20:31.520 --> 20:33.280
- Here, cheers.
- Cheers.

20:33.440 --> 20:34.280
- Here!
- Here.

20:34.360 --> 20:35.760
- Here.
- Let's drink to it.

20:35.840 --> 20:37.440
Ms. Weiwei, let's drink to it.

20:37.520 --> 20:40.920
Here, cheers.

20:44.120 --> 20:45.080
Here, Nai!

20:46.280 --> 20:47.880
Get me some food.

20:49.080 --> 20:49.920
Hold this.

20:50.640 --> 20:53.480
- Here, Houzi, let's drink.
- Let's drink to it.

20:53.560 --> 20:54.400
Drink!

20:56.840 --> 20:59.480
Ms. Weiwei, I'm telling you,

20:59.560 --> 21:02.280
this is Nai's first romantic relationship.

21:02.360 --> 21:05.800
He has no experience.
You have to be nice to him.

21:06.920 --> 21:10.440
Plus, it's just too hard
for computer majors

21:10.520 --> 21:12.240
to find a good wife.

21:25.200 --> 21:27.600
When Nai grabbed my hand,

21:27.680 --> 21:30.200
he didn't seem like a newbie at love.

21:31.520 --> 21:36.040
Mrs. Nai, what I'm telling you
is all true.

21:36.360 --> 21:40.600
It's true, someone did call Nai
and confessed her love on the phone.

21:41.320 --> 21:46.280
She also said something about the gala.
Everyone knows what she's trying to do.

21:47.760 --> 21:51.080
Her name is something Meng...

21:53.560 --> 21:55.680
She called Nai yesterday, too.

22:00.960 --> 22:03.240
I'm done. I'm drunk.

22:06.040 --> 22:08.720
You can't only reveal half of the gossip!

22:11.240 --> 22:12.600
She said she wanted to explain something.

22:14.120 --> 22:16.200
Could it be about Ai Chanel?

22:16.920 --> 22:19.120
Why did she need to explain to Lord?

22:20.320 --> 22:22.600
- And then?
- That's it.

22:26.200 --> 22:27.280
Mrs. Nai,

22:27.640 --> 22:32.680
Nai is an assassin. He's cold-blooded.
One sentence ends the conversation.

22:32.920 --> 22:35.680
Right? How can you treat a girl like that?

22:36.440 --> 22:39.320
It's next to impossible
for computer majors

22:39.400 --> 22:40.960
to get a call from a girl.

22:42.400 --> 22:43.400
Nai is always like that.

22:44.520 --> 22:45.480
Aren't you drunk?

22:45.560 --> 22:48.320
Are you kidding? I was acting.
Don't take it seriously.

22:48.400 --> 22:51.480
Anyway, you think I'd get drunk from this?
You're funny.

22:53.480 --> 22:57.640
So, after all this, what did Lord say?

22:58.360 --> 23:02.160
Guess! Take a guess as to
what your Lord said.

23:05.080 --> 23:07.640
He said, "Who's this?"

23:17.600 --> 23:19.360
Isn't this normal conversation?

23:19.720 --> 23:21.920
Anyone who gets an unfamiliar call

23:22.000 --> 23:23.320
would ask, "Who's this?"

23:26.960 --> 23:28.160
Well...

23:28.520 --> 23:31.800
It turns out,
this C girl is the campus belle.

23:32.560 --> 23:35.680
Yep, I'm 70 to 80 percent sure,
that it's her.

23:36.080 --> 23:38.840
Nai, we hacked
that Chanel girl's computer.

23:39.320 --> 23:41.480
It's finals time.
She's got to have a term paper on there.

23:41.560 --> 23:43.680
We hacked her computer, and...

23:46.080 --> 23:48.840
- Moral character is essential in a man.
- What do you mean?

23:49.200 --> 23:53.000
You're usually a smart guy.
How come your IQ is so low?

23:53.680 --> 23:55.320
Nai is calling you crass.

23:55.720 --> 23:58.040
So we just forget about the forum thing?

23:58.120 --> 24:00.600
No! It's not like you don't know Nai well.

24:00.680 --> 24:02.160
What is Nai's style?

24:02.840 --> 24:04.400
Don't you know how he is?

24:04.480 --> 24:05.440
How is he?

24:05.920 --> 24:08.480
Often... inhuman.

24:16.080 --> 24:17.440
They've had too much to drink.

24:18.040 --> 24:20.800
That's what I think, too.

24:23.560 --> 24:27.240
Bro, why didn't you order more dishes?

24:27.320 --> 24:29.840
Bro, you have to watch your image.

24:29.920 --> 24:32.760
It's the first time we computer majors
are having dinner with a girl.

24:32.840 --> 24:36.520
- Image. Get it?
- Bro, does Mrs. Nai count as a girl?

24:36.840 --> 24:39.400
Mrs. Nai's gaming image
is one of fierceness.

24:40.000 --> 24:41.480
Everyone thought
she was a guy in disguise, okay?

24:42.120 --> 24:44.040
On top of that, what's a girl?

24:44.320 --> 24:47.000
A girl is a limited resource
to be fought over.

24:47.640 --> 24:49.920
Mrs. Nai already has Nai.

24:50.280 --> 24:52.840
Now, she's considered the third gender.

24:53.400 --> 24:55.440
Why would you care about your image?

24:55.800 --> 24:57.360
That does make some sense.

24:59.280 --> 25:02.760
We need more dishes.
Let's get a Sichuan Blood Pudding,

25:02.840 --> 25:05.480
a Spicy Crab, a Chili Crawfish,

25:05.560 --> 25:08.640
and Fish Head with Chili Sauce.

25:08.720 --> 25:11.080
Remember, it has to be spicy.
The spicier, the better.

25:11.880 --> 25:14.200
Don't make it spicy.
Nai doesn't like spicy food.

25:15.280 --> 25:18.120
He's treating us to dinner.
He can watch us eat.

25:18.200 --> 25:19.400
Make it spicy.

25:21.760 --> 25:24.840
Lord doesn't like spicy food? No way!

25:24.920 --> 25:27.920
He seemed to be enjoying himself,
when we had Sichuan Boiled Fish.

25:28.000 --> 25:29.840
He didn't wince one bit.

25:30.080 --> 25:31.040
You...

25:32.640 --> 25:33.800
No.

25:56.440 --> 25:59.840
Aren't you bored, Nai,
playing by yourself?

26:00.480 --> 26:02.800
Look, Mrs. Nai has been sitting there
for so long.

26:03.000 --> 26:05.560
She's bored to death.
You should let her play.

26:06.880 --> 26:08.040
Sure.

26:11.800 --> 26:14.720
I... I don't know how.

26:15.240 --> 26:17.600
It's my first time at a pool hall.

26:19.720 --> 26:20.880
I'll teach you.

26:38.080 --> 26:38.920
Lower your body.

26:56.160 --> 26:57.080
Focus.

27:08.400 --> 27:11.520
It went in! Am I gifted?

27:11.960 --> 27:12.840
Pretty good.

27:29.560 --> 27:34.000
Very technical. Absolutely spot on.
She'll go far.

27:34.440 --> 27:38.760
Nai, let's take Ms. Weiwei along,
when we come out to play.

27:40.240 --> 27:41.560
There won't be a next time.

27:41.720 --> 27:42.760
Why not?

27:43.240 --> 27:44.960
I'll install a pool table at home.

27:47.880 --> 27:49.160
It's about time.

27:50.080 --> 27:53.480
Weiwei has a curfew.
I'm taking her back. You guys go ahead.

28:05.800 --> 28:06.680
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

28:06.760 --> 28:07.600
Bye-bye!

28:12.600 --> 28:13.440
What now?

28:13.520 --> 28:14.400
- Let's continue.
- Come on.

28:14.480 --> 28:15.320
- Carry on.
- Come on.

28:32.360 --> 28:34.080
Go on up. See you tomorrow.

28:37.240 --> 28:41.720
Wait, you don't like spicy food.

28:41.920 --> 28:44.400
Why didn't you tell me that day,
when we had Sichuan Boiled Fish?

28:45.560 --> 28:48.640
I remember all the dishes
we ordered were spicy.

28:48.920 --> 28:51.200
We got maximum spicy
on the Sichuan Boiled Fish.

28:51.840 --> 28:55.160
It's fine. I can adjust to the company.

28:58.440 --> 29:00.560
It's okay, if you don't like spicy food.

29:01.200 --> 29:02.560
You don't have to accommodate me.

29:11.760 --> 29:13.160
You don't need to help me out so much.

29:15.880 --> 29:20.840
Refilling water,
buying breakfast for me...

29:22.040 --> 29:23.400
You're not suited to these things.

29:25.920 --> 29:26.800
Weiwei...

29:30.240 --> 29:32.000
It's my first time being with a girl.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.880
I often don't know what to do.

29:36.160 --> 29:42.520
At least for now, I have to be capable
of what others can do.

29:58.600 --> 30:00.040
The doors are closing. Hurry!

30:03.960 --> 30:07.240
Log on to the game later.
I have something for you.

30:09.520 --> 30:10.360
Okay.

30:12.640 --> 30:13.480
Good night.

30:15.720 --> 30:16.600
Good night.

30:21.360 --> 30:22.520
Go on back!

31:04.640 --> 31:09.000
A CHINESE GHOST STORY

31:17.480 --> 31:21.000
I finished it yesterday.
I wasn't in a hurry to give it out,

31:21.440 --> 31:24.520
but now I can't wait to give it to him.

31:51.760 --> 31:52.960
This is for you.

31:56.840 --> 31:59.320
I told you, I'd make up for the dowry.

32:15.480 --> 32:20.240
Aside from the five rare monsters,
I also asked Fengteng

32:21.040 --> 32:25.200
for two rare materials: white jade
and quenched metal.

32:26.080 --> 32:28.360
I made this with the rare materials,
as well as others I'd gathered.

32:30.360 --> 32:32.560
Your old hairpin is already top notch.

32:33.800 --> 32:37.280
I thought I'd try to make something
that's even better.

32:38.560 --> 32:42.480
Are you surprised
that I am fortunate enough?

32:43.720 --> 32:46.000
It's because I have pretty good luck.

32:48.040 --> 32:49.760
Then everything's pretty good.

32:51.920 --> 32:53.280
What am I saying?

32:53.480 --> 32:54.400
Why is it called Hairwei?

32:56.200 --> 32:58.080
It means "hairpin by Weiwei."

33:01.880 --> 33:04.040
If you don't like it, you can change it.

33:04.360 --> 33:08.360
- I'm not artistically-inclined.
- No, I like it a lot.

33:14.160 --> 33:15.760
Bind myself to Weiwei.

33:20.560 --> 33:23.520
Well... I should log off.

33:24.400 --> 33:25.800
I'm a bit tired today.
I want to get some rest.

33:28.840 --> 33:30.080
Thank you, missus.

34:20.520 --> 34:21.760
Why is it called Hairwei?

34:23.000 --> 34:25.600
It means "hairpin by Weiwei."

34:27.679 --> 34:29.840
If you don't like it, you can change it.

34:30.120 --> 34:34.840
- I'm not artistically inclined.
- No, I like it a lot.

34:38.840 --> 34:41.280
Banshan,
you didn't study idioms in vain.

34:41.360 --> 34:43.639
- Of course! Open the door.
- Okay, here.

34:48.960 --> 34:52.760
Nai, it's a beautiful night,
and you had a beautiful girl

34:53.000 --> 34:54.120
Why are you back before us?

34:56.159 --> 34:57.400
Why don't we play cards?

34:57.480 --> 35:00.560
Did I hear you right, Nai? Cards?

35:01.760 --> 35:05.160
It's nothing. I'm in a good mood.
I want to play.

35:06.680 --> 35:09.400
I've been on a roll.
You guys better watch out.

35:09.480 --> 35:10.560
No welching afterwards!

35:10.640 --> 35:12.280
- Come on!
- All right!

35:12.360 --> 35:13.920
Houzi, clear the table.

35:16.800 --> 35:19.200
Watch this! Three queens and two threes.

35:21.520 --> 35:23.440
Four twos and one ace.

35:26.080 --> 35:27.080
No welching!

35:33.840 --> 35:35.880
- Nice!
- Sweet!

35:35.960 --> 35:40.120
It was Nai's treat tonight,
but you picked up the tab.

35:41.160 --> 35:43.760
Says who? The night is young.

35:43.880 --> 35:44.960
Another round!

35:45.040 --> 35:46.600
- Come on.
- All right.

36:36.720 --> 36:39.800
I don't want to enter society
heavily indebted.

36:43.680 --> 36:44.680
Write it.

36:45.680 --> 36:46.800
For real?

36:47.680 --> 36:48.880
Yes.

36:56.560 --> 36:58.000
Fine, I'll write it.

36:59.000 --> 37:00.480
I.O.U.

37:00.960 --> 37:03.520
I, Yu Banshan,

37:03.920 --> 37:08.680
owe Xiao Nai 800 meals.

37:08.760 --> 37:12.720
I'll pay it with labor,
during the summer break...

37:17.040 --> 37:18.800
No, we don't get summer breaks anymore.

37:21.600 --> 37:24.080
For the months of July and August,

37:24.400 --> 37:29.920
I will buy food for Xiao Nai, every day.
Yu Banshan.

37:31.400 --> 37:34.520
Take it! You're so lazy!
It's just running out to get food.

37:34.600 --> 37:38.560
That's right.
We have no more summer breaks.

37:55.360 --> 37:58.280
Goodbye, Qing University.

38:00.800 --> 38:03.120
Goodbye, Qing University.

38:03.200 --> 38:06.400
Bye, Qing University.

38:10.000 --> 38:11.240
My home is on campus.

38:31.800 --> 38:32.720
Goodbye...

38:35.520 --> 38:36.520
Qing University.

38:50.480 --> 38:52.240
Did you catch a cold?

38:52.480 --> 38:55.120
Or is someone thinking about you, Weiwei?

38:55.760 --> 38:57.160
It's just a cold.

39:13.360 --> 39:18.800
It's not a cold.
Someone is totally thinking about you.

39:22.960 --> 39:25.760
It's so nice to have a boyfriend
whose parents are professors.

39:25.840 --> 39:29.520
He can drive on campus. Unlike us!

39:29.800 --> 39:34.520
We have to drag heavy suitcases
all the way to the gates! So annoying!

39:34.920 --> 39:37.000
Hence he's multi-functional Lord.

39:37.400 --> 39:40.920
You're leaving so early, Weiwei.
Is he upset?

39:42.920 --> 39:44.320
I don't think so.

40:15.920 --> 40:17.360
You should go back. See you next semester.

40:19.040 --> 40:21.120
- See you next semester!
- See you next semester!

40:21.200 --> 40:22.160
- Bye-bye!
- Bye-bye!

40:22.720 --> 40:24.160
- Be careful!
- Bye-bye!

40:54.360 --> 40:55.640
Did you bring medicine?

41:01.480 --> 41:03.040
You mean cold medicine?

41:03.680 --> 41:06.800
No, but it's fine.
It's just a slight cold.

41:08.440 --> 41:09.320
COMPOUND CAPSULES

41:10.880 --> 41:11.960
Take this.

41:34.480 --> 41:35.360
This is for you.

41:39.320 --> 41:40.200
New dowry?

41:42.360 --> 41:46.640
It's my cactus.
I can't take care of it during the summer.

41:47.080 --> 41:49.480
So, please look after it for me.

41:51.640 --> 41:52.760
So when I see it, I'll think of you.

41:55.240 --> 41:57.600
I didn't mean to book my tickets so early.

41:58.520 --> 42:03.080
I didn't know you,
when I booked the tickets through school.

42:22.600 --> 42:24.040
I'll get a platform ticket.

42:24.520 --> 42:27.120
It's okay. I'll get on the train myself.

42:31.280 --> 42:33.720
The luggage is heavy.
Missus, please sit down for a while.

45:11.920 --> 45:14.360
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
